---
const text =
  'To ensure that hospitals were scored fairly, we began by analyzing each hospital across 19 metrics for <strong>patient experience, quality outcomes,</strong> and <strong>patient safety.</strong> Then, we went a step further and tested 100,000 different ways to measure hospital quality. Hospitals that consistently produced good results received the Reliable Excellence Indicator. <strong>Only around 250 hospitals receive this distinction.</strong> You can rely on those hospitals to provide high-quality excellent care, again and again.';
---

<aside class="reliable-excellence" aria-labelledby="reliable-excellence-title">
  <h2 id="reliable-excellence-title">Reliable Excellence Indicator</h2>
  <p set:html={text}></p>
</aside>

<style>
.reliable-excellence {
  position: relative;
  width: min(calc(100% - 2rem), 888px);
  margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  padding: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
  border-radius: 2rem;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(118, 224, 204, 0.25), transparent 38%),
    var(--color-blue-2);
}

.reliable-excellence::before,
.reliable-excellence::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -1.5rem;
  left: 1.5rem;
  width: 3rem;
  height: 3rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
}

.reliable-excellence::before {
  background: var(--color-green-1);
}

.reliable-excellence::after {
  background: white;
  mask-image: url('/icons/icon-award.svg');
  mask-position: center;
  mask-repeat: no-repeat;
  mask-size: 1.5rem;
}

h2 {
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
  color: var(--color-blue--4);
  font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.65rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.15;
}

p {
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
  max-width: 64rem;
  color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-text) 84%, white);
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.08rem);
  line-height: 1.65;
}

p :global(strong) {
  color: var(--color-blue--4);
  font-weight: 800;
}

@media (min-width: 700px) {
  .reliable-excellence::before,
  .reliable-excellence::after {
    left: -1.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
}
</style>
